{% set preApplicationText %}
		{% if applicationData.anticipatedDateOfSubmission %}
			The application is expected to be submitted on {{ applicationData.anticipatedDateOfSubmission | date }}.
		{% endif %}
		{% if not applicationData.anticipatedDateOfSubmission and applicationData.anticipatedSubmissionDateNonSpecific %}
			The application is expected to be submitted in {{ applicationData.anticipatedSubmissionDateNonSpecific }}.
		{% endif %}
{% endset %}

{% if preApplicationText | length %}
	<p class="govuk-body">
		{{ preApplicationText }}
	</p>
{% endif %}

<p class="govuk-body">
	When we receive the application, we have 28 days to decide whether to accept it for examination.
</p>

<p class="govuk-body">
	If we accept the application, you will then be able to register to have your say and view all the application
	documents.
</p>

